  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/a3cba57bcebe92cffdcbe299f5ae0431.avif?t=1739554016\" width=800 height=134 /></span><br>Join the cute Bumballon on this frantic adventure in a colorful world full of dangers! Fast, fun and very charismatic. Face various obstacles to save the Ballon's kingdom and its beautiful Princess Moon.<br><br><strong>Characteristics <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/5f6c82cf9c53f34cac26c77ed82efea7.apng?t=1739554016\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/5f6c82cf9c53f34cac26c77ed82efea7.poster.avif?t=1739554016\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=16 /></picture></span> </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Beautiful animated graphics.<br></li><li> Explore 7 worlds with that taste of retro gaming nostalgia.<br></li><li> Fun and challenging achievements!<br></li><li> 35 different levels and charismatic enemies.<br></li><li> 5 unlockable skins for the most powerful jewel explorers.<br></li><li> Several mechanics.</li></ul><br><strong>Bumballon is a game for those who like challenges where many times each death is a lesson to overcome obstacles.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/83e4247c7cacaf18a17937ce6e53ef76.poster.avif?t=1739554016\" width=544 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/83e4247c7cacaf18a17937ce6e53ef76.webm?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/83e4247c7cacaf18a17937ce6e53ef76.mp4?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore the world in search of lost relics and swap for new skins.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/b6d48e49de80f3048c5943f4ce824462.poster.avif?t=1739554016\" width=542 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/b6d48e49de80f3048c5943f4ce824462.webm?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/b6d48e49de80f3048c5943f4ce824462.mp4?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Show off your precision skills and become the fastest hero in the Ballon's kingdom to save Princess Moon!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/6d6c13faac41df06f29b026f446f53c7.poster.avif?t=1739554016\" width=540 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/6d6c13faac41df06f29b026f446f53c7.webm?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750490/extras/6d6c13faac41df06f29b026f446f53c7.mp4?t=1739554016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
